Submission Link: https://summit.apple.com/conferences/1/submissions/new

Contact: mls-contact@group.apple.com

Instructions: 
- The ML Summit Committee will review each submission and select based on innovativeness, quality, and the work’s impact at Apple.
- Material presented at the summit should not require specific project disclosures.
- Abstracts should be in PDF format and no longer than one page. 

- Abstracts should contain: 
(1) Sufficient information for summit committee not familiar with the specific work to appreciate the innovation and impact of the work.
(2) The key idea/concept behind the work and complexity of the issue that the work is addressing.
(3) A summary of the results and impact. Also indicate what shipping product the work is included in, if any. 

- Choose preferred format: full-talk, lightning-talk, or poster/demo
*Full-talks: 30min. For some exception cases we will consider longer duration.
*Lightning-talks: 5 mins
